            , the constable, produced the copper, which was deposed to by the two last witnesses).</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I am not guilty of the crime I am charged with.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called one witness, who had known him sixteen years, and who gave him an excellent character. GUILTY (Aged 36.)</p>
